  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为团队权限系统画一个类图，核心是要表达清楚用户、角色、权限和团队这四者之间的关系。用户可以通过直接分配或者通过角色间接获得权限。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "Role",
        "Permission",
        "Team"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，这是一个典型的RBAC模型加上团队隔离。我先确认一下：Team是作为一个组织单元，下面挂多个Role和Permission，然后User再和Role、Permission建立多对多关系？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Team",
        "Role",
        "Permission",
        "User"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，一个团队下面可以有多个角色和多个权限。用户和角色是多对多，用户和权限也是多对多——有些权限可以直接给用户，有些是通过角色继承的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Team",
        "Role",
        "Permission",
        "User"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把四个核心类建出来：User、Role、Permission、Team。Team先放简单的id和name字段。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Team"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Permission类需要name、guard_name和team_id三个字段，name是权限标识，guard_name是守卫名称，team_id做团队隔离。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Permission"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Permission类已添加，包含name、guard_name、team_id。Role类我打算放name、guard_name、team_id，另外加上权限管理的方法：givePermissionTo、revokePermissionTo和syncPermissions。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Permission",
        "Role"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "Role的方法没问题，syncPermissions是用来批量同步权限的吧？参数应该是Permission数组。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Role",
        "Permission[]",
        "syncPermissions"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，我写成syncPermissions(Permission[])。现在处理User类，这里方法比较多：assignRole、removeRole、syncRoles、hasRole，还有直接判断权限的hasPermissionTo和通过角色判断的hasPermissionViaRole。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "Role",
        "Permission",
        "assignRole",
        "removeRole",
        "syncRoles",
        "hasRole",
        "hasPermissionTo",
        "hasPermissionViaRole"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "hasPermissionViaRole这个命名我再确认一下，意思是通过所属角色间接拥有该权限，对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "hasPermissionViaRole",
        "Role",
        "Permission"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，就是检查用户的任一角色是否拥有该权限。现在来画关联关系：Role和Permission是多对多，用\"many\"标注两端。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Role",
        "Permission",
        "many"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "关系名用\"has\"就可以，表示角色拥有权限。然后User和Role也是多对多，同样标注\"many\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "Role",
        "many",
        "has"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "User和Role的多对多关系已添加。User和Permission也需要直接的多对多关系，给那些不通过角色的直接权限。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "Permission",
        "many"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，直接权限和角色权限是两条线。最后Team的关系：一个Team对应多个Role，一个Team对应多个Permission，都是一对多。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Team",
        "Role",
        "Permission",
        "1",
        "many"
