      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "深色主题可以，但我要确认一下：Role的givePermissionTo和revokePermissionTo参数是单个Permission，而syncPermissions是数组，这个区分对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
