      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，givePermissionTo(Permission)和revokePermissionTo(Permission)是单条操作，syncPermissions(Permission[])是批量覆盖。User的syncRoles同理，参数是Role[]。",
      "elements_involved": [
